OL,4,Cleft mum in the dark about daughter's
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FCardiff and Vale University Health
OL,8,FBoard said it is "committed to
OL,9,Fproviding accessible communication"
OL,10,Fand offers a "variety of
OL,11,Finterpretation options" including face-
OL,12,Fto-face and a 24-hour video and phone
OL,13,Fservice, while the "small number of
OL,14,Finstances" where in-person
OL,15,Finterpreters have not been available
OL,16,Fis due to the "national shortage and
OL,17,Fout of its control".
