OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FAt such a worrying time, keeping
OL,8,Finformed about her daughter's
OL,9,Fcondition has been crucial, but Rachel
OL,10,Fsays the University Hospital of Wales
OL,11,Fhas repeatedly failed to provide her
OL,12,Fwith an interpreter, and on one
OL,13,Foccasion, she claims doctors wanted to
OL,14,Foperate on Anwen without an
OL,15,Finterpreter there.
