OL,7,FA spokesperson from Cardiff and Vale
OL,8,FUniversity Health Board said: "We
OL,9,Fremain committed to providing
OL,10,Faccessible communication to all our
OL,11,Fpatients and their families. British
OL,12,FSign Language (BSL) is our third most
OL,13,Frequested language. Whilst there is a
OL,14,Flimited number of BSL interpreters
OL,15,Facross Wales, we work to utilise in
OL,16,Fperson interpretation and 24/7 access
OL,17,Fby ensuring staff and patients are
OL,18,Faware of the availability interactive
OL,19,Fservices via staff communication
OL,20,Fmechanisms.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
