OL,7,FPolly Winn, external affairs manager
OL,8,Ffor Wales at RNID (Royal National
OL,9,FInstitute for Deaf People), said:
OL,10,F"We're calling for this to be taken
OL,11,Fmore seriously essentially because
OL,12,Fthis is undermining people's
OL,13,Ffundamental rights, and we have seen
OL,14,Fnew guidance published in September
OL,15,Fthat is much stronger, but we want to
OL,16,Fsee now is accountability for health
OL,17,Fboards who don't meet those needs, and
OL,18,Falso much better training for staff."
OL,20,FCardiff and Vale University Health
OL,21,FBoard's response in full:
