OL,7,FA spokesperson said: "The health board
OL,8,Foffers a variety of options accessible
OL,9,Fto staff for interpretation support
OL,10,Fincluding face to face, and a 24/7
OL,11,Fvideo and telephone support service to
OL,12,FBSL users. We have installed a Virtual
OL,13,FRelay Service on Pelican Ward in the
OL,14,FChildren's Hospital of Wales and are
OL,15,Fworking closely with partners to roll
OL,16,Fout this service across the UHB.
