OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"We are keen to promote more deaf
OL,8,Fawareness training for staff and
OL,9,Fcontinue to work with the local
OL,10,Fcommunity and the British Deaf
OL,11,FAssociation to improve experiences for
OL,12,Four patients.
OL,14,F"Across Anwen's stay in our hospitals,
OL,15,Fwe have provided in excess of 350
OL,16,Fhours of in-person interpretation
OL,17,Fsupport supported at all times with
OL,18,Finterpretation devices available. We
OL,19,Fprovided a device to be used on
OL,20,Fdischarge as well to support ongoing
OL,21,Fcommunication.
