OL,7,F"We appreciate there were a small
OL,8,Fnumber of instances where in-person
OL,9,Finterpretation services have not been
OL,10,Favailable due to the national
OL,11,Fshortage. This is sadly outside of the
OL,12,Fhealth board's control. It is
OL,13,Fappreciated that having an unwell
OL,14,Fchild will always cause anxiety and
OL,15,Fany communication difficulties make
OL,16,Fthis more difficult.
